sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / DSP API
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WFC as workflow-controller<br/>9090/TCP metrics<br/>6060/TCP healthz
    participant StepPod as Step Pod
    participant ArgoExec as argoexec (sidecar)<br/>UID: 2000
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DB as PostgreSQL / MySQL<br/>5432/TCP or 3306/TCP<br/>(optional)

    Note over User, DB: Flow 1: Workflow Execution

    User->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8s-->>WFC: Watch event (informer)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    WFC->>K8s: Create Step Pod<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>StepPod: Pod scheduled

    activate ArgoExec
    Note over ArgoExec: Init Phase
    ArgoExec->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>Auth: Access key / IAM
    S3-->>ArgoExec: Artifact data

    Note over StepPod: Execute user container
    StepPod->>StepPod: Run workflow step

    Note over ArgoExec: Wait Phase
    ArgoExec->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>Auth: Access key / IAM
    S3-->>ArgoExec: Upload confirmation
    ArgoExec->>K8s: Patch pod annotations<br/>(WorkflowTaskResult CR)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    deactivate ArgoExec

    WFC->>K8s: Update Workflow status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User, DB: Flow 2: Workflow Archival (Optional)

    WFC->>DB: Archive workflow history<br/>Auth: Username/password<br/>Encryption: TLS (configurable)
    DB-->>WFC: Archive confirmation
    WFC->>K8s: Label workflow as archived<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User, DB: Flow 3: CronWorkflow Scheduling

    Note over WFC: Cron worker evaluates<br/>CronWorkflow schedule<br/>(sync period: 10s)
    WFC->>K8s: Create Workflow from<br/>CronWorkflow spec<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    WFC->>K8s: Update CronWorkflow status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
